description.content:
Note: Kindly message me before ordering to avoid cancellation.


Dear Customer, 


Happy to see you here.-:) 


Do you need to develop a mobile app for your restaurant and grocery business? Id like to be considered for your project. Im a strategic mobile apps developer with a strong background in developing various sorts of applications, including Native apps, Hybrid apps, web apps, and other Dedicated web and Generic mobile apps. 


I can develop the interference that exactly represents your brand and appeals to your target audience. Whether you need a formal, serious tone or a more playful one, I can make the transition with the ease of your choice in an impressive way.


I am accustomed to working with all sorts of applications and services and in a variety of android/iOS development.


Here will be the list of features that I can integrate into your application:


-Location-Based Delivery

-Restaurant Management

-Food Categories.

-Offer Section

-Coupon Section

-Wallet Options

-Payment Gateways


I have a deep passion for research and guarantee that all of my work is 100% original


Thanks

questionsAndAnswers.question: 1) How to search city wise restaurant?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To search restaurants in particular city is very simple . Enter preferred city name in search bar and click on search. All restaurant listed in searched city will be display.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How to login to Admin Panel?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Every restaurant owner has their own admin panel from where owner can manage their restaurant details. For login to admin panel of restaurant, restaurant owner have to go to their restaurant page. Owner have to click on Restaurant Login to login in admin panel of restaurant.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide maintenance services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we are well-known for providing full-cycle solutions. From conceptualization to post-sale support and maintenance, we will stay with you at every stage and ensure that your app is bug-free and stays so in the future.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What technologies do you guys work on?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
We work on all latest and trending technologies which includes both web and mobile app development.

Web : PHP/ Wordpress/ Magento/ CakePHP/ Zend/ YII/ Laravel/ Codeignitor/ AngularJS/ NodeJS

Mobile : iPhone native/ Android native/ IONIC/ Phonegap/ React Native

questionsAndAnswers.question: What should be my server requirement?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Depend on traffic expectations, server company and server parameters can be defined which can range in $10 USD to $100 USD per month.
